{"tid":725500,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞被狂「抽水」！兩大主力中堅手球送12碼  打NBA？","createTime":"2018-07-01T16:56:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T17:19:53.000Z","uid":147522,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3487c6cb96f1cb28e8dbb84e8765d7df9defde48","tid":725500,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T16:56:47.000Z","msg":"　　世界盃16強西班牙對陣東道主俄羅斯，比賽第40分鐘，比基禁區內手球，球證吹射12碼。關於這次12碼判罰，西班牙媒體《馬卡報》認為球證判罰正確。<br />\n<br />\n　　當時，尤巴角球混戰中頭槌攻門打在比基伸起的手上，球證判射12碼，尤巴親自主射命中，1-1。《馬卡報》的球證專家安杜哈爾-奧利弗對此表示：「比基可以不用把手揚起來。他高高舉起手臂，阻擋了俄羅斯的射門，非常明顯的12碼。」<br />\n<br />\n　　<br />\n　　有意思的是，比基的球會隊友安迪堤在法國與澳州的比賽，也曾在禁區內故意手球，讓對手獲得了一粒12碼。"},{"pid":"6df2de3cac67089ab27031f68ec24c8da0e91d48","tid":725500,"uid":105838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T16:57:16.000Z","msg":"轉去打排球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e46dc55f79a03e95a27c01524a3f8ab425d74e","tid":725500,"uid":166413,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T16:59:58.000Z","msg":"big gay 以為打歐聯咩，可以黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25536018f4d6d4d4737232bfab030f9ec1b79b3c","tid":725500,"uid":5649,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T17:02:10.000Z","msg":"踢巴塞邊會吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe5acd04fa11fd952be38b2a507d275737d6aa3","tid":725500,"uid":49144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T17:02:57.000Z","msg":"Big gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1b0153ab13f1ba6d1a1f6d858f39a4b563647d","tid":725500,"uid":27882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T17:03:30.000Z","msg":"多謝碧基體諒,俾全體西班牙隊友可以提早放暑假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b916a59bc9cf335f08d5ae068a5f020638303cc","tid":725500,"uid":21447,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"